OL,3,CChris Whitty to be questioned on 'stay
OL,4,Cat home' messaging at Covid inquiry
OL,6,FEngland's chief medical officer is to
OL,7,Fbe quizzed on the impact the pandemic
OL,8,Fhad on the NHS.
OL,10,FProfessor Sir Chris Whitty is to face
OL,11,Fquestions when he appears before the
OL,12,FUK Covid-19 Inquiry on Thursday.
OL,14,FInquiry chairwoman Baroness Heather
OL,15,FHallett is examining the impact of the
OL,16,Fcrisis on NHS workers, patients and
OL,17,Fthe delivery of healthcare.
