OL,6,FSir Chris, who became a well-known
OL,7,Ffigure during the crisis due to his
OL,8,Fregular appearances at Downing Street
OL,9,Fpress conferences, is likely to be
OL,10,Fasked about the "Stay Home, Protect
OL,11,Fthe NHS, Save Lives" messaging
OL,12,Fdeployed at the start of the pandemic.
OL,14,FFormer chief nursing officer for
OL,15,FEngland Dame Ruth May was asked about
OL,16,Fthe messaging when she appeared before
OL,17,Fthe inquiry earlier in the month.
