OL,6,FAsked if the message "got the balance
OL,7,Fwrong", she replied: "In hindsight I
OL,8,Fwish it was, 'stay at home but not if
OL,9,Fyou're pregnant'... in hindsight, yes."
OL,11,FIt comes as a charity said the
OL,12,FGovernment "missed opportunities" to
OL,13,Fsupport the nation's mental health
OL,14,Fduring the pandemic.
