OL,6,FA report from the Centre for Mental
OL,7,FHealth said the pandemic caused
OL,8,F"collective trauma" from the effects
OL,9,Fof isolation, bereavement and fear,
OL,10,Fand longer term trauma of health care
OL,11,Fworkers and the psychological legacy
OL,12,Famong children and young people of
OL,13,Fdisrupted education.
OL,15,FAndy Bell, chief executive of the
OL,16,Fcharity and co-author of the report,
OL,17,Fsaid: "The Covid-19 pandemic has hit
OL,18,Fthe nation's mental health hard.
