OL,3,CChris Whitty to be questioned on 'stay
OL,4,Cat home' messaging at Covid inquiry
OL,6,F"A lack of government planning, and
OL,7,Fthe absence of any strategy to
OL,8,Fmitigate harms, meant that both short-
OL,9,Fterm and long-lasting mental health
OL,10,Fharms occurred that are still visible
OL,11,Ffour years on.
OL,13,F"It is truly shocking that people with
OL,14,Fa mental illness were so
OL,15,Fdisproportionately affected by the
OL,16,Fvirus itself, exacerbating existing
OL,17,Fhealth inequalities and widening the
OL,18,Falready vast life expectancy gap.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
