OL,3,CChris Whitty to be questioned on 'stay
OL,4,Cat home' messaging at Covid inquiry
OL,6,F"In the wake of the Darzi review,
OL,7,Ftoday's report is yet more evidence
OL,8,Fthat the NHS requires system-wide
OL,9,Fchange to meet rising levels of need
OL,10,Ffollowing the pandemic.
OL,12,F"We call on the Covid public inquiry
OL,13,Fand the UK Government to take the
OL,14,Fevidence we have amassed seriously and
OL,15,Fensure that we learn the right lessons
OL,16,Ffrom the pandemic about its
OL,17,Frelationship with the nation's mental
OL,18,Fhealth.
